üìÇ Navigation
cd                  :: shows current directory
cd folder_name      :: goes inside a folder
cd ..               :: goes back one folder
cd D:\MyApp         :: directly jumps to a specific path
D:                  :: switches to D drive
E:                  :: switches to E drive
dir                 :: lists all files and folders
cls                 :: clears the terminal screen


üìÅ Folder & File Management
mkdir MyApp         :: creates a new folder
rmdir MyApp         :: deletes an empty folder
rmdir /s MyApp      :: deletes a folder with all files inside
type nul > app.py   :: creates an empty file
del app.py          :: deletes a file
rename app.py main.py :: renames a file
move app.py backup\ :: moves file to another folder
copy app.py test.py :: copies a file


üìÑ View & Edit Files
type main.py        :: shows full content of a file
type main.py | more :: shows file content page by page
notepad main.py    :: opens file for editing
find "print" main.py :: searches word inside a file


üß† History & Utilities
doskey /history     :: shows previously typed commands
tree /f             :: shows folder structure as a tree
where python        :: shows python installation path


üêç PYTHON COMMANDS
python              :: opens python interactive mode
python main.py      :: runs a python file
pip install requests :: installs a python package


üß™ VIRTUAL ENVIRONMENT (venv)
Create venv
python -m venv venv :: creates a virtual environment

Activate venv
Command Prompt
venv\Scripts\activate :: activates venv in CMD

PowerShell
.\venv\Scripts\Activate.ps1 :: activates venv in PowerShell

Deactivate venv
deactivate          :: exits virtual environment

Delete venv
rmdir /s venv       :: deletes virtual environment folder
